Kurog (Normal)
-----------------
|cffff7c0aHERO ON PULL|r

2. P2 Frost add {skull} must stay kicked
3. Kurog does a frontal cone - don't be in it.
4. Good fight for a kick-focus macro

Frost > Fire > P2 > Earth > Storm > P2 > Storm > Enrage

<{square} FROST Altar> 0-65 energy
-- |cff00ffffAbsolute Zero|r |cffffff00[Soak]|r Bring to melee for soaks
-- |cff00ffffFrigid Torrent|r |cffffff00[Orbs]|r Dodge the balls

<{star} FIRE Altar> 65-100 energy
-- |cff00ffffSearing Carnage|r |cffffff00[Dance]|r stutter-step to avoid small swirlies.
-- |cff00ffffMagma Burst|r |cffffff00[Pools]|r drop behind raid, near {square}Frost

<PHASE 2a>
{cross} <Destroyer> |cff00ffffFrost Binds|r |cffffff00[Kick]|r "I've got next"
-- <Destroyer> |cff00ffffFreezing Tempest|r |cffffff00[Stack]|r Ticking dmg > 10 yards
{skull} <Fiend> Dodge lava pools

<{circle} EARTH Altar> 50-100 energy
-- |cff00ffffErupting Bedrock|r |cffffff00[Quakes]|r Dodge expanding rings
-- |cff00ffffSesmic Rupture|r |cffffff00[Adds]|r cleave adds down
-- |cff00ffffEnveloping Earth|r |cffffff00[Heal absorb]|r Heroic only? Maybe Hero here?

<{diamond} STORM Altar> 0-50 energy
-- |cff00ffffShocking Burst|r |cffffff00[Bombs]|r get big circles out of raid
-- |cff00ffffThunder Strike|r |cffffff00[Soak]|r 1-2 players soak small circles
-- |cff00ffffLightning Crash|r |cffffff00[Zaps]|r spread, don't share.

<PHASE 2b>
{skull} <Crusher> |cff00ffffGround Shatter|r |cffffff00[Bombs]|r get out of raid
-- <Crusher> |cff00ffffViolent Upheaval|r |cffffff00[Dodge]|r Avoid the pillars
{cross} <Tempest> |cff00ffffLethal Current|r |cffffff00[AoE DoT]|r GTFO, focus heals.

{T}<Tanks>
